    <h1 class="text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>
        At CozyCrib, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your data when you use our platform.
    </p>

    <h4> Information We Collect</h4>
    <p>To enhance your experience, we collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, profile details, and payment information.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Device details, IP address, browser type, operating system, and site interaction data.</li>
        <li><strong>Transaction Details:</strong> Booking history, payment transactions, and refund requests.</li>
        <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> If enabled, we may collect real-time location information to improve our services.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4> How We Use Your Information</h4>
    <p>We process your data to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Facilitate property bookings, payments, and customer interactions.</li>
        <li>Ensure platform security and prevent fraudulent activities.</li>
        <li>Personalize your experience based on preferences and past interactions.</li>
        <li>Provide customer support and communicate important updates.</li>
        <li>Analyze usage patterns to optimize platform performance.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4> Data Security and Protection</h4>
    <p>
        We implement robust security measures, including data encryption and secure servers, to protect your personal information. While we strive to ensure the highest level of security, we encourage users to take precautions, such as using strong passwords and keeping login credentials confidential.
    </p>

    <h4> Sharing Your Information</h4>
    <p>We may share your information with trusted third parties, including:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Payment processors, customer support teams, and analytics partners.</li>
        <li><strong>Legal Authorities:</strong> When required by law to comply with legal obligations or enforce our terms.</li>
        <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In the event of a merger, acquisition, or asset sale, your information may be transferred accordingly.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4> Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h4>
    <p>
        We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance user experience and analyze platform performance. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.
    </p>

    <h4>Data Retention</h4>
    <p>
        Your personal data is retained for as long as necessary to fulfill business and legal requirements. You may request data deletion through your account settings or by contacting us.
    </p>

    <h4> Your Rights and Choices</h4>
    <p>
        As a CozyCrib user, you have the right to access, modify, or delete your personal information. To exercise these rights, please reach out to us at <strong>support@cozycrib.com</strong>.
    </p>

    <h4> Policy Updates</h4>
    <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any revisions will be posted on this page, and continued use of CozyCrib signifies your acceptance of the changes.
    </p>
